sequenceDiagram
  autonumber
  actor User
  participant Browser as WarGamingModeClient
  participant Hook as useWarGamingBootstrap
  participant API as GET /api/war-gaming/bootstrap
  participant Handler as handleWarGamingBootstrapGet
  participant DB as SQLite

  User->>Browser: Open /war-gaming/{mode}?target=...
  Browser->>Hook: mount + refresh()
  Hook->>API: GET /api/war-gaming/bootstrap
  API->>Handler: handleWarGamingBootstrapGet()
  Handler->>DB: loadRuntimeProjection/readOperator/loadDoctrine/loadSourceMap
  DB-->>Handler: rows

  alt bootstrap failure (db/read error)
    Handler-->>API: throw error
    API-->>Hook: 500 {error,traceId}
    Hook-->>Browser: setError("Failed loading War Gaming bootstrap")
    Browser-->>User: Loading failure state
  else bootstrap success
    Handler-->>API: 200 JSON bootstrap payload
    API-->>Hook: payload
    Hook-->>Browser: setData(payload) + session cache write
    Browser-->>User: Render onboarding or WarGaming view
  end
